Cell["\<\
Find the constituent tree and the grammar dependency graph of the following \
sentence:

\[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]A bird flew from a high building\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote]

Is the word \[OpenCurlyDoubleQuote]high\[CloseCurlyDoubleQuote] properly \
classified?\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.779598592065216*^9, 
  3.779598674784704*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"3792f3fb-651c-43d0-824a-\
bbddb6255e2f"]
}, Open  ]],

